quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,10,"Nabii Mucammadow isi marah cus: ku-Rabbi Nabii Muusah seeceeh, firqawni maray daalimiinih yanil gex kaak iyye waqdi"
  26,11,"Usun Firqawni mara, usun Yallih digaalák mameesitaanaa"
  26,12,"Nabii Muusa: yi-Rabbow diggah anu yoo dirabboysaanamak meesita iyye"
  26,13,"Kaadu usun yot aban dirabboysiyyah alil yok ceytaah, ku-farmoh gudduysiyyah arraba yok yaabe waytaamak mceesitak, Jibriil yi-toobokoyta Haaruunû fanah kaa rub farmô gudduysiyyah yoo catamkeh iyye"
  26,14,"Kaadu firqawnaa kee firqawni mari dambi yot-le num keenik qideeh, woo caneh yoo qidaanamak meesita iyye Nabii Muusa"
  26,15,"Yalli Nabii Muusak: Aleey koo maqidaanak, koo kee ku- toobokoyta Nabii Haaruun ni- astooti luk gexa, diggah Nanu catoh siinî luk nan isin ittaanam kee siinil gacsaanam naabbehik iyye"
  26,16,"Tokkel isin firqawnal gexaay, diggah nanu ginô Rabbih nımma farmoyta kinnino kaak ixxica"
  26,17,"Israa-iil xaylo cabaay, nelluk ken Rub kaak ixxica"
  26,18,"Firqawni Nabii Muusak: Ni addal alqih (saldih) anuk koo maqarsinninoo, kaadu maggo liggiditte ku-qumrik ni-addal masuginnitoo?kaak iyye"
  26,19,"Kaadu ku-uma taamay abteh iyya abteh (numtin qidim kinnuk), atu isih aben maqaane yangadde marih numuh anuk"
  26,20,"Nabii Muusa firqawnal gacisak:toysa anu tet abem anu iggima-le marak numuk teynah suge waqdi kaak iyye"
  26,21,"Tokkel anu siinik meesite wagqdi siinik kudeceh, yi-Rabbi nubuwwannu yoh yeceeh, farmoytiitik numuk teyna yoo abe iyye"
  26,22,Woo niqmatay atu yoh guneh lowtaah warissa Israa-iil xaylo naqoosah haysitteemii
  26,23,"Firqawni Nabii Muusal:kaxxamariinitak ginô Rabbi maatiyaay iyye"
  26,24,"Nabii Muusa firqawnal gacisak:usuk Qaranwaa kee baaxooy ken nammayih fanal taniimih Rabbi isin woh yasmite mara tekkeenik keenik iyye"
  26,25,"Firqawni isi derfal tan makaabanak:Muusa yol gacsam taabbeenih innaa? iyye"
  26,26,"Nabii Muusa keenik iyyeh:usuk sin Rabbiiy siinik naharsi abbobtih Rabbi kinni"
  26,27,Firqawni isi marak diggah sin farmoytay sin fan rubsume usuk cabuli kinni iyye
  26,28,"Nabii Muusa:usuk ayrò mawqaa kee ayrò kormaay, ken nammayih fanal taniimih Rabbi isin kas- kassoowa mara tekkeenik keenik iyye"
  26,29,"Firqawni Nabii Muusak yô kalah Yalla haysittek, diggah casbisen marih num koo abeyyo kaak iyye"
  26,30,Nabii Muusa yi-numma tascasseemik baxxaqqa ittam (astooti kinnuk) koh baahennokuv? casbit yoo haytam kaak iyye
  26,31,"Firqawni Nabii Muusak:numma yacee marih num tekkek tet baahey kaak iyye"
  26,32,"Tokkel Nabii Muusa isi caxxa qideeh, usuk (caxxa kinnuk) too waqdi baxxaqqa iyya baadeysa yekke"
  26,33,"Kaadu Nabii Muusa isi gaba isi kamiisik moyya kak culta ikkek culussu heeh edde luk hadiffi heeh, too waqdi is (gaba kinnuk) yable marat qidih ifak raqqa itte baras aalle kalah"